description=Single local MCP (127.0.0.1:8765) Miclaw connects to: proxies the remote sandbox tools (exec/run_background/...) AND serves phone<->sandbox file transfer (push_file/pull_file). initialize() gates on backend reachability. Native Android build, OS DNS+CA.
